Scrol Theme for Shopify

.by Shopledge (www.shopledge.com)
.created April 2011
.version 1.0
.homepage: http://www.shopledge.com/2011/05/04/setting-up-scrol-theme-for-shopify/


Scrol is an elegant theme with focus on presenting as much products and information as possible on the frontpage. 
Supports mobile, smartphone and tablet displays and it is fully customisable -- content, colors and language. 

Every store is unique. We are ready to support your Shopify experience both with design and development. 
Contact us via twitter @shopledge or email contact@shopledge.com

Enjoy your store, Your Shopledge Team. 
